<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF17FF3DFFBAF8F56977F8B8" box="[151,261,1886,1912]" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Clavatula</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF17FF3DFE3BF8F569F6F8B8" box="[278,388,1886,1912]" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Clavatula</emphasis>
)
</taxonomicName>
cf. 
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF17FF3DFE95F8F56A19F8B8" box="[440,619,1886,1912]" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">pseudinterrupta</emphasis>
Peyrot— 
<treatmentCitation id="0A9C10D6FF17FF3DFDF4F8F56C76F8B8" author="Steininger, F." box="[729,1028,1886,1912]" page="438" pageId="149" pageNumber="150" year="1973">
<bibRefCitation id="EFAC4B36FF17FF3DFDF4F8F56C76F8B8" author="Steininger, F." box="[729,1028,1886,1912]" pageId="149" pageNumber="150" pagination="2" refId="ref144701" refString="Steininger, F. (1973) Die Molluskenfaunen des Ottnangien. In: Papp, A., Rogl, F. &amp; Senes, J. (Eds.), M 2 Ottnangien. Die Innviertler, Salgotarjaner, Bantapusztaer Schichtgruppe und die Rzehakia Formation. Chronostratigraphie und Neostratotypen, Miozan der zentralen Paratethys. Vol. 3. Veda, Bratislava, pp. 380 - 615." type="book chapter" year="1973">
Steininger 
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF17FF3DFC7FF8F46BF8F8B8" box="[850,906,1886,1912]" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">et al.</emphasis>
1973: 438
</bibRefCitation>
</treatmentCitation>
.
</treatmentCitationGroup>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8236C7FF17FF3DFFEAF8296899F825" blockId="149.[151,1436,1886,2021]" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">
<bibRefCitation id="EFAC4B36FF17FF3DFFEAF82969BAF85C" author="Steininger, F." box="[199,456,1922,1948]" pageId="149" pageNumber="150" pagination="2" refId="ref144701" refString="Steininger, F. (1973) Die Molluskenfaunen des Ottnangien. In: Papp, A., Rogl, F. &amp; Senes, J. (Eds.), M 2 Ottnangien. Die Innviertler, Salgotarjaner, Bantapusztaer Schichtgruppe und die Rzehakia Formation. Chronostratigraphie und Neostratotypen, Miozan der zentralen Paratethys. Vol. 3. Veda, Bratislava, pp. 380 - 615." type="book chapter" year="1973">
Steininger 
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF17FF3DFE6DF828690AF85C" box="[320,376,1922,1948]" italics="true" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">et al.</emphasis>
(1973)
</bibRefCitation>
mentioned two poorly preserved specimens from the Ottnangian of 
<collectingRegion id="49F9F825FF17FF3DFB90F8296D66F85C" box="[1213,1300,1922,1948]" country="Germany" name="Bayern" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Bavaria</collectingRegion>
(
<collectingCountry id="F32A7657FF17FF3DFA0FF8296DE2F85C" box="[1314,1424,1922,1948]" name="Germany" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Germany</collectingCountry>
), which have not been illustrated. As stated by the authors, their specimens are not conspecific with the species from 
<collectingCountry id="F32A7657FF17FF3DFFBAF8606895F825" box="[151,231,1995,2021]" name="France" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">France</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C327654CFF14FF3EFFEAFF3C6A9BFEDD" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B8236C7FF14FF3EFFEAFF3C6A9BFEDD" blockId="150.[151,1436,151,285]" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">
<bibRefCitation id="EFAC4B36FF14FF3EFFEAFF3C6916FF71" author="Rutsch, R. F." box="[199,356,151,177]" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" pagination="1 - 77" refId="ref142946" refString="Rutsch, R. F. (1929) Die Gastropoden des subalpinen Helvetien der Schweiz und des Vorarlbergs. Abhandlungen der Schweizerischen Palaontologischen Gesellschaft, 49, 1 - 77." type="journal article" year="1929">Rutsch (1929)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAC4B36FF14FF3EFEBBFF3C6ABAFF71" author="Pfister, T. &amp; Wegmuller, U." box="[406,712,151,177]" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" pagination="151 - 209" refId="ref141347" refString="Pfister, T. &amp; Wegmuller, U. (2007) Gastropoden aus den Belpberg-Schichten (Obere Meeresmolasse, mittleres Burdigalium) bei Bern, Schweiz. 2. Teil: Tonnoidea bis Architectonicoidea. Archiv fur Molluskenkunde, 136, 151 - 209. https: // doi. org / 10.1127 / arch. moll / 0003 - 9284 / 136 / 151 - 209" type="journal article" year="2007">Pfister &amp; Wegmüller (2007)</bibRefCitation>
described several specimens from the Burdigalian of 
<collectingCountry id="F32A7657FF14FF3EFA22FF3C6DEAFF71" box="[1295,1432,151,177]" name="Switzerland" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">Switzerland</collectingCountry>
, which they assigned to 
<taxonomicName id="4C3D4D44FF14FF3EFEB0FF106B64FF14" box="[413,790,187,213]" class="Gastropoda" family="Clavatulidae" genus="Clavatula" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="jouanneti" subGenus="Perrona">
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF14FF3EFEB0FF106A79FF15" box="[413,523,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">Clavatula</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF14FF3EFD31FF106A0AFF14" box="[540,632,187,212]" italics="true" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">Perrona</emphasis>
) cf. 
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF14FF3EFD81FF106B64FF14" box="[684,790,187,212]" italics="true" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">jouanneti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF14FF3EFC0BFF106B37FF14" box="[806,837,187,212]" italics="true" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">sic</emphasis>
] (Des Moulins) (in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAC4B36FF14FF3EFB09FF106CAFFF15" author="Rutsch, R. F." box="[1060,1245,187,213]" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" pagination="1 - 77" refId="ref142946" refString="Rutsch, R. F. (1929) Die Gastropoden des subalpinen Helvetien der Schweiz und des Vorarlbergs. Abhandlungen der Schweizerischen Palaontologischen Gesellschaft, 49, 1 - 77." type="journal article" year="1929">Rutsch 1929: 14</bibRefCitation>
, pl. 1, fig. 2) and to 
<taxonomicName id="4C3D4D44FF14FF3EFF99FF74692CFF39" box="[180,350,223,249]" class="Gastropoda" family="Clavatulidae" genus="Clavatula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="undefined-1">
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF14FF3EFF99FF746950FF39" box="[180,290,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">Clavatula</emphasis>
sp. 1
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C3D4D44FF14FF3EFEB9FF746A4CFF39" box="[404,574,223,249]" class="Gastropoda" family="Clavatulidae" genus="Clavatula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="undefined-2">
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FF14FF3EFEB9FF746A70FF39" box="[404,514,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">Clavatula</emphasis>
sp. 2
</taxonomicName>
(in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAC4B36FF14FF3EFD46FF746BBFFF39" author="Pfister, T. &amp; Wegmuller, U." box="[619,973,223,249]" pageId="150" pageNumber="151" pagination="151 - 209" refId="ref141347" refString="Pfister, T. &amp; Wegmuller, U. (2007) Gastropoden aus den Belpberg-Schichten (Obere Meeresmolasse, mittleres Burdigalium) bei Bern, Schweiz. 2. Teil: Tonnoidea bis Architectonicoidea. Archiv fur Molluskenkunde, 136, 151 - 209. https: // doi. org / 10.1127 / arch. moll / 0003 - 9284 / 136 / 151 - 209" type="journal article" year="2007">Pfister &amp; Wegmüller 2007: 176</bibRefCitation>
, pl. 11, figs 9–21). The poor preservation of these specimens does not allow any identification.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
